Package de.oth.blocklib.disasters.volcanos

Class VolcanoData

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.disasters.volcanos.VolcanoData
public class VolcanoData
extends java.lang.Object
An class that is used to represent volcanos that should be able to erupt multiple times. These are managed by the VolcanoManager.
Author:
Tobias Mueller
